{"tid":1790994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記唔記得有個人一直默默耕耘搞工會？","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T16:21:38.000Z","uid":185999,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2aaaf997fb2773988af13f2114c5bb1f31a412","tid":1790994,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解仲未入工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星火被拉<br />\n貼牆被拉<br />\n老師被停職<br />\n當共軍政府每日步步進逼<br />\n香港人連買贖罪卷嘅機會都已經用完<br />\n<br />\n停止外判抗爭<br />\n積極組織工會<br />\n時機一到<br />\n發動無限期罷工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係我哋作為和理非對呢個城市嘅交代</span><br />\n<br />\n三罷 tg<br />\n@hkonstrike<br />\n<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F663&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=917886d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike/663</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F669&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f55eb3ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike/669</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=a57b87e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=22896388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"http://bit.ly/33hmGRR\"